quran[8{c,v,t}:
27,56,"magar uss ki qoum ka jawab is ke siwa kuch nah tha ke unhon ne kaha"" nikaal do loot ke ghar walon ko apni bastii se, yeh barray pakbaaz bantay hain """
27,57,"aakhir-kaar hum ne bacha liya uss ko aur uss ke ghar walon ko, bajuz uss ki biwi ke jis ka peechay reh jana hum ne tey kar diya tha"
27,58,"aur brsayi unn logon par aik barsaat, bohat hi buri barsaat thi woh unn logon ke haq mein jo mutnabba kiye ja chuke thay"
27,59,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) kaho, hamd Allah ke liye aur salam is ke unn bundon par jinhein is ne bargzida kya ( inn se pucho ) Allah behtar hai ya woh mabood jinhein yeh log is ka shareek bana rahay hain ?"
27,60,"bhala woh kon hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko peda kya aur tumahray liye aasman se pani barsaya phir is ke zareya se woh khushnuma baagh ugaye jin ke darakhton ka ugana tumahray bas mein nah tha? kya Allah ke sath koi dosra khuda bhi ( inn kamon mein shareek ) hai? ( nahi ), balkay yahi log raah e raast se hatt kar chalay ja rahay hain"
27,61,"aur woh kon hai jis ne zameen ko jaye qarar banaya aur is ke andar darya rawan kiye aur is mein ( pahoron ki ) maikhain garh den aur pani ke do zkhiron ke darmain parday haail kar diye? kya Allah ke sath koi aur khuda bhi ( inn kamon mein shareek ) hai? nahi, balkay inn mein se aksar log nadaan hain"
27,62,kon hai jo be qarar ki dua santa hai jabkay woh ussay pukare aur kon is ki takleef rafa karta hai? aur ( kon hai jo ) tumhe zameen ka khalifa banata hai? kya Allah ke sath koi aur khuda bhi ( yeh kaam karne wala ) hai? tum log kam hi sochte ho
27,63,aur woh kon hai jo khushki aur samandar ki tarikeon mein tum ko rasta dekhata hai aur kon apni rehmat ke agay hawaon ko khushkhabri le kar bhejta hai? kya Allah ke sath koi dُosra khuda bhi ( yeh kaam karta ) hai? bohat baala o bartar hai Allah is shirk se jo yeh log karte hain
